172
00:07:48,489 --> 00:07:50,210
ahistorical fantasy pastiche.

173
00:07:50,577 --> 00:07:53,239
But to me, the idea of simply having the ruler now

174
00:07:53,239 --> 00:07:55,820
be a woman instead of a man without changing

175
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,901
any of the underlying politics or perspectives

